#: ../../networking.rst:5
msgid "Networking"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:7
msgid ""
"Each instance (or server) of ``covid-ht`` can network with others to "
"share data and improve their classification service."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:9
msgid "Under this context, instances are called *Nodes*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:11
msgid ""
"Networking is done through the :ref:`rest_api`. Every service that "
"implements it accordingly can network with the instance."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:13
msgid ""
"Each node has an unique identifier, the **CHTUID** (*Covid-HT Unique "
"IDentifier*) - a case-sensitive 5 characters alphanumeric string that "
"will identify the instance in network - set in the :setting:`CHTUID` "
"setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:15
msgid ""
"Node creation and configuration is done with the admin interface "
"(``/admin/base/networknode``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:18
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:20
msgid "Besides a unique name, each Node has:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:22
msgid ""
"an internal user (User) and unit (Unit) associated with it for the "
"incoming data from sharing if enabled, and"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:23
msgid ""
"an external user (Remote User) with an authentication token (Remote User "
"Token) for sending data to the node if sharing is enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:25
msgid ""
"The internal user should have an Authentication Token (generated in the "
"admin interface - ``/admin/authtoken/tokenproxy/``) which should be "
"provided to the node in order to be able to send data."
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:28
msgid "Data Sharing"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:30
msgid ""
"If enabled, Data created within the local node will be sent to the "
"external node based on the mode selected:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:32
msgid "On Update"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:33
msgid "Will send the Data each time a record get created or updated"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:35
msgid "On Finished"
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:35
msgid "Will send the Data only when it is marked as \"Finished\""
msgstr ""

#: ../../networking.rst:37
msgid ""
"Each node will propagate that Data through its network also, this is "
"where the ``CHTUID`` becomes strictly neccesary to identify where the "
"Data was created - Data from a node's unit may not be created by the node"
" but propagated by it."
msgstr ""

